Record Class CardMapRecord

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
it.polimi.ingsw.CommunicationProtocol.ServerClient.DataTransferObjects.CardMapRecord
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public record CardMapRecord(Map<Coordinates,CardVisibilityRecord> cardsPlaced, List<Coordinates> availablePlacements, Map<Artifacts,Integer> artifactsCounter, List<Coordinates> coordinatesPlaced) extends Record implements Serializable
Represents a record containing information about a card map in a game.

A CardMapRecord consists of the cards placed on the map, available placements for cards, artifacts and their counts, and the coordinates of the placed cards.

This record implements the Serializable interface to support serialization.
